      <section eId="sec_CC-3042">
        <num>CC 3042</num>
        <heading>3042. Â Commercial suretyship</heading>
        <subsection eId="CC-3042__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The surety is engaged in a surety business;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3042__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The principal obligor or the surety is a business corporation, partnership, or other business entity;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3042__subsec_3">
          <num>(3)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The principal obligation arises out of a commercial transaction of the principal obligor; or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3042__subsec_4">
          <num>(4)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The suretyship arises out of a commercial transaction of the surety.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
